description: Updates the specified event with a new label.

parameters.name: eventId
parameters.description: The ID of the event associated with the label to update.

parameters.name: eventTypeName
parameters.description: The event type of the event associated with the label to update.

parameters.name: assignedLabel
parameters.description: The new label to assign to the event.

parameters.name: labelTimestamp
parameters.description: The timestamp associated with the label. The timestamp must be specified using ISO 8601 standard in UTC.
